overview: Cécile Dumont, daughter of the President of the Republic, is kidnapped by a group of criminals wishing to erase their debts to the State but not only. They also want the resignation of the leader of the nation. Alas, the dear little girl is not the one expected and cunning with perverse tricks to turn the situation in her favor. Quickly joined in her cell by a local marginal just as vicious as herself. They both succeed in making their confinement naughty and sexually pleasant ...
title: The President's Daughter
